        <li>Document type analysis and sample review</li>
        <li>Accuracy requirement definition</li>
        <li>Volume and throughput assessment</li>
        <li>ROI calculation and recommendation</li>
        <li>Risk mitigation: Know exactly what you're getting before committing to development</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="service-tier">
