      <p><strong>Investment: $8,000 - $15,000</strong></p>
      <p>We build a working proof-of-concept system for a single document type, demonstrating real-world accuracy on your actual documents.</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Custom extraction logic for your document type</li>
        <li>Two-stage prompting implementation</li>
        <li>Accuracy testing on sample dataset</li>
        <li>Human-in-the-loop workflow design</li>
        <li>Working demo using your real documents</li>
